ad aloud to us, I can't recall - any specific instances, but doubtless they would do on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5711905\charrsid11812698 occasion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
