 used to go down there 'til the war broke out in 1914 and of course that - that finished any holidaying - for a time anyway.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11212422\charrsid11812698 
