No, father used to exercise his - his talent for photography. He used to like to take groups of us on Sunday. He often - o
ften did that. Sunday afternoon after dinner we always used to walk over to Newcastle to Sunday school. Either coming home again after Sunday school - or going to - for tea - to an aunt in Newcastle and then we should go back to - chapel in the evening yo
u see. Otherwise I say we should come home after Sunday school and - we should stay at home at night. When our parents went to - chapel perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid155753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11212422\charrsid11812698 Did they go every Sunday?
