No. No. Or miracles. I know - it's easy to say that - things happen that - appear to be miracles but - I should say there's always a - there's always a - a reason for it even if we don't know the reason. That is of course -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid155753 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11212422\charrsid11812698 I always thought Unitarians were somewhat connected towards Methodists?

